{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": " 第3话 100014033",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "等等，你这是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "当然是字面意思。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "卡珊德拉，\\n我打算把圣城内关于\\n“起始之人”的研究交给你来统筹。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "以你的能力，\\n一定比我更能将大家的研究成果\\n运用到决战之中。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "等一下。为什么要交给我？\\n这不是少爷在做的事吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我想你应该能够明白吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "已经恶化到这种程度了吗……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "你再坚持几天。\\n我一定会在这期间\\n找到治疗的方法。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "没有那个必要。\\n我已经放弃与死亡对抗了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "那我就能眼睁睁地看着\\n他留在这世上的骨肉\\n这么死去吗！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "卡珊德拉……放弃吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "我可不会让你说出\\n“放弃”这两个字的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "法尔艾斯王兄必须\\n接受我们香榭利亚\\n医疗部队的医治。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯……\\n医疗部队是？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哦呵呵！\\n你以为我听说王兄时日不多\\n以后会袖手旁观吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我把南格拉斯迪亚大陆、北大陆、\\n太吾和日出之国等\\n世界各地的医生都召集到了香榭利亚……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "这支部队可以说是\\n集结了全世界的所有医疗技术。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你的人脉可真是广啊。\\n这外交手段确实让人瞠目结舌。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "不只是医生，\\n我也动员了香榭利亚研究部所有力量\\n准备了最新的医疗设备。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "王兄，\\n请务必随我去\\n香榭利亚接受治疗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "虽然我对你说的医疗部队很感兴趣，\\n但还是把他们用在今后的战斗中吧。\\n用在我身上也是白费。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我不认为是白费。\\n治好王兄才是今后的战斗中\\n不可或缺的一步。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我就算是绑也要把你\\n绑上巨舰·瑰丽号。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯，不要再任性了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我这不是在任性，\\n而是做出了身为王族应有的判断。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "王兄的知识和智慧\\n将是决战的关键。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "无论我们拥有多么强大的战力，\\n计策都始终是决定性因素之一。\\n为了胜利，我必须要让你活下去。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "不是还有你吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "王兄你不仅有着多年以来\\n研究积累的知识，\\n更有着身为“起始之人”傀儡之时的记忆。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我觉得没有人比王兄更适合\\n当这次决战的军师了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "身为王族，需要正确地判断\\n如何运用每一条生命，不是吗？\\n自然也包括你自己的生命……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "你现在倒是学会掩饰\\n自己那套感情论了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "哎呀，到底是谁在掩饰呢？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我这不是感情论，\\n而是在陈述客观事实。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我本就不是应该活到现在的人，\\n按理说，我早该死掉才对。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "抗拒死亡所带来的结果……\\n看着眼下的情况，\\n你还不明白吗。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "那我问你……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你以为你这样接受死亡\\n就算是赎罪了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你真的是甘心\\n接受死亡吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "回答我，王兄。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "法尔艾斯大人！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "利弗！\\n我们正在谈论要事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "无妨。\\n利弗，你说吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "抱歉打断您的谈话。\\n巴尔加海姆那边来了一件\\n给您的紧急传令……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "巴尔加海姆？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "莱昂尼多王兄那边发生什么了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "据说巴尔加海姆遭到了\\n大量魔兽和来路不明的龙的袭击。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100018_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗",
            "context": "龙身上都带有庞大的黑暗魔力，\\n而莱昂尼多大人为了\\n与其对抗正在苦战之中。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "原来如此……所以才会传信于我，\\n要我在他抵抗的这段时间\\n想出应对黑暗魔力的方法对吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯，用巨舰·瑰丽号\\n带我去巴尔加海姆……\\n咳咳！唔！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "王兄！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卡珊德拉",
            "context": "法尔艾斯少爷！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "哈啊……哈啊……我没事。\\n谢斯……快带我去巴尔加海姆……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "你都这样了还要去前线，\\n简直就是自杀！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "今后的决战之中……\\n是我的生命重要，\\n还是莱昂尼多的生命重要？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我现在不去助阵，\\n若是莱昂尼多发生意外，\\n我方的战力将会大幅度下降。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "这是无论如何都要避免的……\\n莱昂尼多才是决战之中不可缺少的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "身为王族，需要正确地判断\\n如何运用每一条生命……不是吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯……\\n做出王族该有的判断吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我知道了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "利弗，立刻组建援军前往巴尔加海姆。\\n卡珊德拉，研究部队就交给你了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110337_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "利弗&卡珊德拉",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "谢斯，虽说你已经\\n是一个成熟的淑女，\\n但心软这一点还是没有改变啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "我不想听你这些话……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "啧……没完没了了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "抱歉我来迟了，莱昂尼多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，让我等这么久。\\n谢斯呢？\\n你不是乘巨舰·瑰丽号来的吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "我让她去部署香榭利亚的防卫了。\\n万一我们打了败仗，\\n那边也一定会受到牵连。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "但我就是为了避免这种“万一”\\n才叫你来的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "包在我身上吧。只要想办法\\n解决那些黑暗魔力就可以了吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "帮我出出主意吧。\\n不能再任由\\n那些家伙继续肆虐了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100014_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法尔艾斯",
            "context": "嗯。我会想办法尽快解决的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}